eds. <PERSON> Gilbert </PERSON> and <PERSON> Sullivan </PERSON> collaborated on 14 works over 25 years, including `` The <ORGANIZATION> Pirates </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> of </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Penzance </ORGANIZATION>,'' `` The Mikado'' and `` H.M.S. Pinafore.'' Other companies, professional and amateur, perform the Savoy Operas, as the works are known. But the <ORGANIZATION> D'Oyly </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Carte </ORGANIZATION> company is the only one devoted entirely to them.
