 <PERSON> Barry </PERSON> <PERSON> Schweid </PERSON>, head of the <ORGANIZATION> AP </ORGANIZATION>'s <ORGANIZATION> State </ORGANIZATION> <ORGANIZATION> Department </ORGANIZATION> staff, accompanied <PERSON> Shultz </PERSON> on his trips to the <LOCATION> Middle </LOCATION> <LOCATION> East </LOCATION> and <LOCATION> Moscow </LOCATION>.
