land, I thought at least I could swim.'' The passengers appeared calm after they landed on <LOCATION> Maui </LOCATION>, said <PERSON> Kevin </PERSON> <PERSON> Hildebrant </PERSON>, a tour driver who helped take the injured to <LOCATION> Maui </LOCATION> Memorial Hospital. `` They were overly calm, I guess, to compensate for what they went through,'' he said.
